"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:2.19.7\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">2.19.7</span> 标题：撞城槌（battering ram）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：חֶרֶב</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：cherev)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek26:9\">EZK 26:9</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：כַּר</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：kar)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek4:2\">EZK 4:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek21:27\">EZK 21:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek21:27\">EZK 21:27</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：קְבֹל</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：qvol)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek26:9\">EZK 26:9</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：ἑλεόπολις</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：heleopolis)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc13:43\">1MA 13:43</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc13:44\">1MA 13:44</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：κριός</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：krios)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc12:15\">2MA 12:15</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述和用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0401_battering_ram.jpg\" alt=\"亚述人用大型有轮撞城槌攻击敌方城墙，双方弓箭手互相发箭（尼姆鲁德（Nimrud），约公元前865-860年；大英博物馆）\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">亚述人用大型有轮撞城槌攻击敌方城墙，双方弓箭手互相发箭（尼姆鲁德（Nimrud），约公元前865–860年；大英博物馆） (Chris0, British Museum, Public domain, via Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>撞城槌是一根原木或者其他长而重的木头，一端用金属包裹，士兵用它来对着城墙或城门猛力撞击。有些撞城槌带有一个尖头，为要在城墙上撞出一个洞；其他撞城槌的末端是钝头。进攻者通过反复撞击城墙，使得城墙逐渐削弱并最终倒塌，或者在墙上撞开一个缺口。在槌头穿透城墙之后，士兵会将撞城槌来回撬动，直到那部分的城墙倒塌。撞城槌可以由士兵抓住摆动，有时也用绳索吊在一个可以移动的木塔上。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻译</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>如果目标语言没有表示“撞城槌”的词语，翻译者可以采用一个描述性的短语。<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek26:9\">EZK 26:9</a> 可译为“他必带着粗重的原木来撞穿你的城墙”（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Century Version\">NCV</abbr> 直译），或“他必派遣军兵用大梁木撞倒你的墙”（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> 直译）。不过，如果译作“他们会使用重型武器猛击你的城墙”（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Italian Common Language Version\">ITCL</abbr> 直译），可能会让现代读者产生误解。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek26:9\">EZK 26:9</a> 中出现希伯来文<em>cherev</em> ，这个词通常表示“剑”，然而根据这里的上下文，这种解释不太可能。在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:25\">EXO 20:25</a> ，同一个词语表示“凿子”（“chisel”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> ）之类的东西。在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek26:9\">EZK 26:9</a> 这节经文中，该词似乎是指一件沉重的铁制工具，可以用来破坏石头墙。沃克斯提出，这是一种带尖头的撞城槌，或者是挖地道工兵使用的一种镐头。各个译本有不同的译法，例如“斧”（“axes”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised English Bible (1989)\">REB</abbr> ）、“铁棒”（“iron rods”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Century Version\">NCV</abbr> ）、“铁条”（“iron bars”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Century Version\">NCV</abbr> ），以及“武器”（“weapons”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New International Version (1984)\">NIV</abbr> ）。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
